{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-attorney-page-js","path":"/our-attorneys/sopian-sitepu","webpackCompilationHash":"c74dd45f1204014f46ad","result":{"data":{"attorneysYaml":{"admissions":["Deputy Chairman of PERADI Lampung","Deputy Chairman of KADIN Lampung"],"bioProfile":"<p>Sopian Sitepu is the head of the general department at Sopian Sitepu and Partners. He has successfully handled litigation and dispute resolution cases across highly diverse sectors. He is a widely recognized lawyer for handling criminal cases; such as fraud, white collar crime, homicides, and forestry. </p> <p>Furthermore, he is in charge of many private law areas such as a general corporate; mortgage, hire purchase, labor dispute, and infrastructure case. He has represented prominent companies in a variety of proceedings and transactions which includes land acquisition and project financing. Sopian Sitepu has represented many notables and major companies such as PT. Tripanca Group, PT. PTPN VII, Toyota Astra Finance, PT. Central Pertiwi Bahari, and more.</p> <p>His background as a lecturer in a public university supports his career in understanding and solving each case comprehensively; in addition, his dedication in law enforcement has flourished as he maintains Legal Aid known as LBH Nasional established since 1996, which helps people in despair who need legal assistance.</p>\n","educations":["Universitas Sumatera Utara, S.H","Universitas Indonesia, M.H","Universitas Diponegoro, M.Kn","Universitas Airlangga, Law Faculty, Dr (cand)"],"firstName":"Sopian","lastName":"Sitepu","position":"Founding Partner / Attorney","slug":"sopian-sitepu","quote":"\"Always bet on justice. It takes a lot of time and resources to win a case against big defendants, and some cases are easier to win than others. But this doesn’t matter at Arnold & Itkin. We take the cases that we must win because it’s the right thing, the ones we have to win—even if it’s hard. <em class=\"em\">Especially if it’s hard.<